cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about end-to-end speech recognition using self-attention via the Transformer architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and speech recognition. The paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound), and the use of residual connections, which could fall under cs.LG (Learning). Additionally, the paper involves training and optimization of neural networks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
